 />\n我聽過佢講talk<br />\n呢位醫生好有心</blockquote><br />\n醫管局要奶共<br />\n咪會俾壓力講真話既醫生囉</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n其實有料既又真係唔撚洗驚醫管局</blockquote><br />\n最多唔撚做啫<br />\n<br />\n外國一定要佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但香港又少一個真心為香港嘅人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93ebbb712333b0ffed0b06a38a5871590dc3fbf","tid":320271,"uid":112200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"香港d醫生都唔見得好好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10個有9個都係差唔多 <br />\n講下病情俾病人聽好似殺你屋企人咁 一係就兜幾千萬個圈"},{"pid":"a8935610a48ea598c6a274b87caebb845e31302b","tid":320271,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}